--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  DATE: 2026-03-16  |  VERSION: 26.03.16.T (Dev)  /  26.03.16.P (Prod)
  TASK: Full project scaffold + feature build — Angular Admin Dashboard
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OVERVIEW
  Project "GetGogi Admin Dashboard" scaffolded from scratch using Angular CLI 17.
  Standalone component architecture adopted throughout. All routes are lazy-loaded.
  SCSS with shared design tokens in src/styles.scss for unified theming.
  API proxy configured via proxy.conf.json for CMS backend calls.

PROJECT STRUCTURE ESTABLISHED
  src/
    app/
      app.component.ts        — Shell: sidebar nav, highlight band, utility bar
      app.routes.ts           — Lazy-loaded route registry with AuthGuard
      app.config.ts           — Angular providers + HTTP client bootstrap
      mocks/
        mock-menu-items.ts    — Fallback dataset when useMockMenuApi = true
      models/
        menu-item.model.ts    — MenuItem interface, CrudAction type, MenuItemPayload
        order-list-item.model.ts — OrderListItem, OrderHeadDetail, OrderStatus union
        soup-menu-item.model.ts  — SoupMenuItem interface (supplemental menu type)
      services/
        auth.guard.ts         — CanActivate guard using localStorage 'authToken'
        menu.service.ts       — CRUD read/write for main menu items via REST
        menubv.service.ts     — Menu service variant (BV location/view)
        menups.service.ts     — Menu service variant (PS location/view)
        orders-list.service.ts — Fetch orders by status, full detail, status updates

ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
  environment.ts (DEV)
    production          : false
    version             : '26.03.16.T'
    useMockMenuApi      : false
    menuApiBaseUrl      : https://api.getgogi.com/api/CMSDemo/Menu
    ordersApiBaseUrl    : https://api.getgogi.com/api/CMSDemo/Orders
    ordersStatusChangeApiUrl: https://api.getgogi.com/api/CMSDemo/Orders/Update_OrderStatus
    defaultLogin        : admin
    defaultPassword     : [set in environment file]

  environment.prod.ts (PRODUCTION)
    production          : true
    version             : '26.03.16.P'
    All API URLs        : same as DEV (same backend, same credentials)

ROUTES REGISTERED (app.routes.ts)
  /                   → redirects to /overview
  /login              → LoginComponent       (public)
  /overview           → OverviewComponent    (guarded)
  /menu-manager       → MenuManagerComponent (guarded)
  /menu-list          → MenuListComponent    (guarded)
  /menu-listps        → MenuListpsComponent  (guarded)  [PS variant]
  /menu-listbv        → MenuListbvComponent  (guarded)  [BV variant]
  /marketing          → MarketingComponent   (guarded)
  /orders             → OrdersComponent      (guarded)
  /order-list.components → OrdersListComponent (guarded)
  /customers          → CustomersComponent   (guarded)
  /customer-list      → CustomerComponent    (guarded)
  /settings           → SettingsComponent    (guarded)
  /**                 → redirects to /overview

